  "Dragon Mage Armor": {
    "index": 1,
    "category": "artifice",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Dragon Mage Armor"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "My magic has made me the powerful being that I am. My words make mountains collapse and my movements bring my opponents to their knees. But I don't have enough. Why should I still bow to the gods when I can be one myself?"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With the \"Ritual of the Dragon Mage Armor\" I can upgrade my armor to a Dragon Mage Armor. This already offers a fairly high level of protection, but I can still improve it. With Upgrade Glyphs I can add some more abilities to the armor. From Fly to Damage Boost, the Upgrade Glyphs offer the potential!"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "Depending on which armor I upgrade, I already have some glyphs installed. See \"Ritual of the Dragon Mage Armor\" for more information."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "Another way to optimize the armor's potential is with the \"Fusion Ritual\", which can combine the power of my spells with the power of my armor."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "While I have to put on full armor to use their effects, all runes seem to be installed only on the chestplate."
        }
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "manaweaving_altar",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:manaweaving/abyssal_dragon_mage_chestplate"
      },
      {
        "type": "manaweaving_altar",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:manaweaving/arch_dragon_mage_chestplate"
      },
      {
