  "Ritual of the Dragon Mage Armor": {
    "index": "0",
    "category": "rituals",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Ritual of the Dragon Mage Armor"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With this ritual I can upgrade my faction armor to Dragon Mage Armor."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "I must wear my full faction armor to perform this ritual. This is then fused with the power of the dragons and becomes the Dragon Mage armor. Enchantments are carried over."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "It seems to me that I can only start the ritual if I have maxed out my magic skills. In other words, I have to be level 75 to use this ritual."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "Depending on which faction armor I use, different starting upgrades will be installed."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With the Spellweaver Robes, I get the Fly I, Mana Boost V, and Mana Regen V upgrades"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With the Druid Robes I get the Elytra II, Fly II, Health Boost I and Kinetic Resistance I upgrades."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With the Infernal Armor, I get the Explosion Resistance I, Fire Resistance II, Meteor Jump I, Movement Speed III, and Jump Boost III upgrades."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With the Witherbone Armor, I get the Damage Resistance I, Mana Regen II, Mist Form I and Water Breathing II upgrades."
        }
      }
    ,
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "(The initial upgrades of each faction can be adjusted in the config.)"
        }
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/dragon_mage_ritual"
      }
    ]
  },
  "Fusion Ritual": {
    "index": "0",
    "category": "rituals",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Fusion Ritual"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "In order to use the full potential of my Dragon Mage Armor, I should fuse it with my spells."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With this ritual I can combine up to 2 spells with my armor. One offensive and one defensive. Both spells trigger when I take damage. The offensive spell hits the aggressor, the defensive spell hits me."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "In order to start the ritual, I must wear my full Dragon Mage Armor. When I add the Netherite Sword, the spell is stored as an offensive in my armor. If I leave it out, the spell is for me."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "By performing the ritual again, I can override the corresponding spell."
        }
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/fusion_ritual"
      }
    ]
  },
  "Ritual of Upgrade": {
    "index": "0",
    "category": "rituals",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Ritual of Upgrade"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "The power of my Dragon Mage Armor is not based on the almighty metal of the armor, but on the runes on it."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "With this ritual I can add upgrade glyphs to my armor. Each glyph has a special ability that transfers to my armor. I can read about this on the relevant upgrade glyphs page."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "However, it is important to note that upgrade glyphs each have a level and a tier."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "The level determines the strength of the glyph, e.g. Fly II lets you fly faster than Fly I. In order to put a higher level glyph on your armor, I need to have the previous glyph installed as well, e.g. I can only install Fly II on my armor if I have Fly I."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "The tier on the other hand gives a statement of which ritual tier I must use to affix the glyph to my armor, e.g. Fly I is Tear 2. Accordingly, I have to use the Ritual of Upgrade at least at tier 2 in order to install the glyph. Which tier a glyph has can be read either in the book or by hovering over the item."
        }
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/upgrade_ritual_tier_i"
      },
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/upgrade_ritual_tier_ii"
      },
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/upgrade_ritual_tier_iii"
      },
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/upgrade_ritual_tier_iv"
      }
    ]
  },
  "Ritual of the Phoenix": {
    "index": "0",
    "category": "rituals",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Ritual of the Phoenix"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "I may be strong, but I'm not invincible. Perhaps I should prepare myself to be defeated one day, to rise from my ashes, to defeat those who killed me!"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "This ritual returns me to the spot where my former self was murdered."
        }
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/phoenix_ritual"
      }
    ]
  },
  "Ritual of Betrayal": {
    "index": "0",
    "category": "rituals",
    "sections": [
      {
        "type": "title",
        "value": "Ritual of Betrayal"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "My faction brought me to where I am today. But isn't my potential higher? Couldn't I reach more? Is my faction holding me back? Maybe I should free myself from this burden."
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "json": {
          "text": "WARNING: With this ritual I free myself from my faction. But I'm also losing every step I've made since then!"
        }
      }
    ],
    "related_recipes": [
      {
        "type": "ritual",
        "location": "dragonmagicandrelics:rituals/betrayal_ritual"
      }
    ]
  },


